Gilbert Pratt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gilbert_Pratt 0 Gilbert Pratt (February 16, 1892 – December 10, 1954) was an American film director, actor and writer. He directed 87 films between 1917 and 1936. He was born in Providence, Rhode Island, and died in Los Angeles, California.
